         * auto glyphs = scaled_font.textToTextGlyph(x, y, text);
         * cr.showTextGlyphs(glyphs);
         * -----------------
         * If no cluster mapping is needed
         * -----------------
         * auto glyphs = scaled_font.textToGlyphs(x, y, text);
         * cr.showGlyphs(glyphs);
